United Continental Holdings' (UAL) CEO Oscar Munoz on Q2 2017 Results - Earnings Call Transcript | Seeking AlphaSign in / Join NowGO»United Continental Holdings' (UAL) CEO Oscar Munoz on Q2 2017 Results - Earnings Call TranscriptJul.19.17 | About: United Continental (UAL) United Continental Holdings, Inc (NYSE:UAL)
Q2 2017 Earnings Conference Call
July 19, 2017 10:30 AM ET
Executives
Julie Stewart - Managing Director of IR
Oscar Munoz - CEO
Scott Kirby - President
Andrew Levy - EVP and CFO
Greg Hart - EVP and COO
Andrew Nocella - EVP and Chief Commercial Officer
Analysts
